## Data Fetching

{{#if appDir}}
- **Server Components**: Fetch directly in components
- **Client Components**: Use SWR or React Query
- **Server Actions**: Handle form submissions
{{else}}
- **getStaticProps**: Static generation
- **getServerSideProps**: Server-side rendering
- **getStaticPaths**: Dynamic routes with SSG
{{/if}}
